id=zdroid_spawnd
name=Zdroid Spawn Daemon
version=v1.0.0
versionCode=1
author=Dylanmurzello
description=Persistent root-context spawn daemon for Zdroid's chroot adapter. One su elevation at boot; per-spawn cost drops from ~200ms (Magisk su mediation queue) to ~5ms (Unix socket + fork+chroot+exec). Required for the "chroot" runtime mode in Zdroid; Zdroid falls back to per-call su without it.
updateJson=https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Dylanmurzello/zed-android-port/main/crates/gpui_android/native/zd-spawnd/magisk-module/update.json
